# Keep source assets tracked. Do not add broad image ignores here;
# assets/tiles/48 and assets/tiles/96 are required for the HTML playable.
!assets/
!assets/tiles/
!assets/tiles/48/
!assets/tiles/48/*.png
!assets/tiles/96/
!assets/tiles/96/*.png
